<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Privacy Policy | Sinister Diesel</title><meta name="description" content="Review how Sinister Diesel collects, uses, protects and updates customer information, including communications and mobile messaging terms."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column sd2-policy-page"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-policy sd2-privacy">
	<section class="sd2-policy__hero"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><nav class="sd2-policy__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Privacy policy</span></nav><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Privacy / Data and communications</p><h1>Your data.<br>Clearly explained.</h1><p>How information is collected, used, protected and updated when you shop, contact support or use Sinister Diesel services.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#privacy-sections">Review the policy</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="help-center.html">Contact support</a></div></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Information use</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Security and service</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Your choices</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="privacy-sections"><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-policy__layout"><aside><p class="sd2-cp__label">Privacy guide</p><h2>Open the section you need.</h2><p>The policy includes communications, service providers, tracking technologies, security, mobile terms and contact information.</p><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="mailto:info@sinisterdiesel.com">Email privacy support</a></aside><article class="sd2-policy__content"><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'prpo_content' )" /></article></div></section>
</main><mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" /></body></html>
